<Content>Extortion If you prefer honesty and open-ness alongside polite service and a welcoming atmosphere -go elsewhere. Do not stay here. I booked this hotel, aware of the good reviews and its central location. I particularly specified breakfast in my booking. I paid 'upfront' and on arrival found that I had 'agreed' to room only. Despite presenting emails confirming the arrangement the receptionists were immovable, rude and resolute. They showed me their version of our email exchanges and some of my email sentences had been ommitted e.g. my requests for breakfast at the time of booking. This seemed very suspect and odd. I contacted the booking agency, via whom I had originally booked, who did their best to rectify the situation but the invisible Berna 'management' were immovable apparently. The agency was powerless, embarrassed and could only apologise. The price I unwittingly paid for room only was extortionate for a hotel of this type. Luckily, we found an excellent government (engineering college) managed cafe across the road which sold solid, robust breakfasts in pleasant, real surroundings, within a little garden area to boot. The ambience here was 100% more appealing here than in the Berna dining area. It came to 13 euros for 3 of us- compared to the 13 euros per head charged for breakfast at the Berna.Check your booking agreement very carefully if you are naive enough, as I was, to book this hotel. You are likely to be misled.One particular male receptionist was extremely surely and supercilious in a most unattractive, unwelcoming and almost threatening way - as if we were doing him a favour staying at the hotel (probably were)! You'll know who he is if you've had the misfortune to stay here.Catalonia Berna - over-priced, unaccommodating and completely lacking in any kind of personal charm whatsoever. You will be treated like a number!To be avoided. Search for a fair, trustworthy hotel that welcomes guests instead of tampering with their email bookings and attempting to rip them off (in my case, successfully) 
